as industrial engineers. As students who
seriously want to prepare themselves for
their chosen profession, it would be to your
best interests if you were to join your Pitt
chapter of the Society for Advancement of
Management. Our school chapter is at pres-
ent composed largely of students in Business
Administration, but it could offer as much
if not more to students in industrial engin-
eering because of the importance and em-
phasis placed on that field by the Society.
